media:group.media:description:
Join Rachel Gurjar in the Bon Appétit Test Kitchen as she prepares her coconut and lemongrass braised short ribs. These short ribs are inspired by Thai flavors, using lemongrass and makrut lime leaves to give an otherwise rich dish a bright, citrusy flavor.&#13;
&#13;
See Rachel's full recipe here: https://www.bonappetit.com/recipe/coconut-and-lemongrass-braised-short-ribs-recipe&#13;
